    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "There's no need to add callbacks to embed_kernel because the eventloop already supports callbacks:\n\n``` python\nimport os\nfrom zmq.eventloop.ioloop import IOLoop\nimport IPython\n\nloop = IOLoop.instance()\n\ndef myfunc():\n    os.system(\"echo hi!\")\n\nloop.add_callback(myfunc)\nIPython.embed_kernel()\n```\n"
  },
